\mathbf v_1
\mathbf v_2
\mathbf D = \text{diag}(\lambda _1, \lambda _2)
\mathbf K = [\mathbf v_1 | \mathbf v_2]
\mathbf D = \mathbf K^{-1} \mathbf A \mathbf K
\mathbf B
\mathbf B^2 = \mathbf A
\mathbf E
